data.description: ***Come VIEW and MAKE an OFFER TODAY!  Incredible SECLUDED HOME located in quite Lucerne Valley CA.  Tucked away near the foothills below Big Bear CA, yet the site is close to paved roads and major highways allowing easy access to all of Southern CA.  Plus, the property is minutes away from the center of town, and only 20 minutes away from newly built shopping centers.  Outside the home has a FENCED 2.07 ACRE LOT ideal for parking RV's, boats, and auxiliary vehicles.  Also included is a SOLAR-POWERED, CODED ENTRY GATE.  In addition, there is low-maintenance desert landscaping, storage shed with shelving, fire-pit, mature shade trees, chicken coops, small garden, and RV HOOK-UPS to water, power, and septic.  Inside the owner has invested tons into the well-kept property.   The nearly 900sf floor plan has a FULLY REMODELED BATHROOM, new paint, new fixtures, new appliances, and new window coverings.  The layout makes the interior feel spacious with large kitchen, and living areas.  The WOOD STOVE keeps things warm in the winter, and there are GORGEOUS VIEWS looking east and west all year round.  As an added bonus the community is part of a small mutual water company where property owners hold SHARES supplying residents with ample inexpensive water.  Honestly, this property offers so much it can't all be listed here, making it a MUST SEE OPPORTUNITY before it's too late.***
